My friend leased office room in building on corner of street in Krnov city...and got keys of entire building too. Rest of building is two floor hotel complex abandoned years ago. I took few photos of inside and outside to make environment as real as possible or at least to make feeling of European city.

Special thanks to will2k for testing and navigation map fixing.

If you like this one, check all of my maps here
This map is also used in my singleplayer mod
